General.Name: Nissan
General.Description: Nissan Medical Industries Ltd, through its subsidiary, engages in the manufacturing and marketing of spunlace non-woven fabrics in the United States, Canada, Europe, and Israel. The company's products are used in reusable and consumable consumer products, medical products, automotive, infrastructure, hygienic, and other industries. It sells its products through its sales agents. Nissan Medical Industries Ltd was incorporated in 1984 and is based in Tel Aviv-Yafo, Israel.
